org.bytedeco.bullet.BulletDynamics

Class btMultiBodySolverConstraint

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.bullet.BulletDynamics.btMultiBodySolverConstraint
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=BulletDynamics.class)
public class btMultiBodySolverConstraint
extends Pointer
    1D constraint along a normal axis between bodyA and bodyB. It can be combined to solve contact and friction constraints.
